            <h3>Founder / President / Programmer</h3>
            <p>Kyle was born and raised in Guelph, Ontario Canada a small city of 114 thousand people. After graduating from high school at Centennial C.V.I. Kyle move to Toronto to pursue a post-secondary education at Seneca College where he studied Small Business Entrepreneurship. Kyle has always had a passion for entrepreneurship from his earliest memories of making a lemonade stand, to selling his toys in garage sales, cutting his neighbour's grass and starting a sole-proprietary DJ business in high school. After graduating from Seneca College Kyle decided to focus on turning his passion for video games into a career. After completing his first year at George Brown College as a Game Programming student he decided to apply his business knowledge to start-up an indie game development studio known today as Grizzly Games.</p>
